Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.50,0:23:14.49,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:20.53,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,在某处呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:26.01,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,温暖的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:29.29,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,从远方传来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:32.35,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,心为之而动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:35.94,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,请告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:42.78,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,这悲伤的预感是否将成真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:49.33,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,未曾知晓的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:56.65,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:24:01.62,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:08.40,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,梦中迷惘 而充满自由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:14.16,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,轻声许下愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.58,0:24:19.65,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,好想和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.59,0:24:28.97,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,相视而笑
